FBIS4-48997 "drchi084_w_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-084 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 HONG KONG & MACAO Hong Kong Preliminary Working Committee Groups To Meet in Hong Kong Preliminary Working Committee Groups To Meet in Hong Kong OW2804160994 Beijing XINHUA in English 1500 GMT 28 Apr 94 OW2804160994 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Hong Kong, April 28 (XINHUA)--The political group and economic groups of the Preliminary Working Committee (PWC) of the Preparatory Committee of the Special Administrative Region of Hong Kong will hold meetings respectively here next week. The political group will meet from May 2 to 3 and the economic group from May 4 to 5. Attending the meetings will be Lu Ping, deputy director and secretary general of the PWC and director of Hong Kong and Macao Affairs Office under the State Council, Zhou Nan, deputy director of the PWC and director of XINHUA NEWS AGENCY Hong Kong branch, as well as other related PWC members. Those PWC members from the mainland will attend the ceremony to inaugurate the HK dollars issurance by Bank of China.
